wikipedia_page.main: Donald Douglas MacPhail (17 February 1911 - 1992) was a Scottish footballer who played for Dumbarton and Dunfermline Athletic in Scotland, for Middlesbrough, Bournemouth & Boscombe Athletic, Carlisle United and Swindon Town in the English Football League, and for South Bank, Burton Town, Nuneaton Town and Dartford in English non-league football.
